text: Cara Cunningham (formerly Chris Crocker; born December 7, 1987) is an American internet celebrity and singer. She is best known for her viral video on video sharing website YouTube. For her video entitled "Leave Britney Alone", she got over 30 million views. She has also appeared on the Maury Povich TV program. Prior to beginning her transition, Cunningham felt she could not be open or public about her gender identify and felt she had to present herself as gay, but she is heterosexual. She often spoken of how hard it was growing up gay or transgender in eastern Tennessee.Chris Crocker hopes to find TV stardom In 2008 Crocker released her first single "Mind in the Gutter".
